      "time_str": "00:35.150",
      "text": "看过你的第一眼",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 38.57,
      "time_str": "00:38.570",
      "text": "就离不开你一切",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 44.52,
      "time_str": "00:44.520",
      "text": "你不懂 这种痛",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 48.21,
      "time_str": "00:48.210",
      "text": "如果这是命 我甘愿去对决",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 54.21,
      "time_str": "00:54.210",
      "text": "你不要最后的选择是拒绝",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 63.31,
      "time_str": "01:03.310",
      "text": "我和他有何分别",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 66.55,
      "time_str": "01:06.550",
      "text": "怎比试爱的强烈",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 70.84,
      "time_str": "01:10.840",
      "text": "掏不空 这种痛",
      "translation": null
